            "verse": 5,
            "text": "each soul will then know what it has sent on ahead and what it has left behind"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "People, what has lured you away from your Lord, the Most Generous"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "He Who created you, formed you, and proportioned you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "In whatever shape He willed, He assembled you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "Yet you still deny the Judgment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "When guardians are standing over you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "honorable recorders"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "They know everything you do"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "Indeed, the truly good will be in bliss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 14,
