        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "They will roast in it on the Day of Judgment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and will never get away from it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 82,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "And how would you know what is the Day of Judgment"
